

 Variables :
 --------------
 
  use :
  -----
  
     --> To represent Object state
     --> To Hold operational data .
     
     
  Types of variables :
  ---------------------
  
  A. by Type ( Data Type )
  -----------------------
  
  a. Primary variables
     
      --> To hold values
  
  b. Reference variables
  
      --> To hold Obj's reference ( address )
      
   ---------------------------------------------------
   
   
   
   1. Primary/primitive  variables
   ========================
   
      a. signed
      
      		i. integral
      		
      			byte ( 8 )
      			short ( 16 )
      			int   ( 32 )
      			long  ( 64 )
      		
      	   ii. real	
      
      b. un-signed
      
      c. boolean
   
      
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
     